<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Good evening Rafaella,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Thank you for taking the time to meet with me last week.<o:p></o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">As discussed, please find attached a process document which outlines t=
he framework of how Tower Insurance will progress your claim.<o:p></o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">This is a framework only and the process will change, as we move throu=
gh each step, given that findings and results will affect the next step in =
the process. This will be a live document that
 will gather detail as we progress.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">However, I do trust that this will give you some insight and knowledge=
 to allow us to participate in the process together.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">I look forward to speaking with you soon.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Please confirm back via email when you get a chance that you agree for=
 Asset Restore to undertake the asbestos survey on the 9<sup>th</sup> &#821=
1; as this is the first step in the process.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Regards,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Grant. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
